item.description:
The event will be held at Pierce Birchmont Camp, on Route 109 E., in Wolfeboro. It should be a lot of fun and a good chance to meet some Carroll County Republicans while enjoying lobster, steamers, corn, salad, hamburgers and hot dogs. If you are available on Saturday please consider attending to show the North Country your support for Ron Paul.

The price is $25 and includes the food mentioned above, along with dessert. Kids 12 and under are free. The contact person is Henry Mock, who can be reached at (603 ) 356 -5109 or majorchip@adelphia.net.
item.name: Carroll County GOP Clambake
